            "description": "Inseparable is a co-operational vertical scrolling platformer, designed to be played on a custom arcade machine via foot controllers, which are similar to these of Dance Dance Revolution. It was made as a group project in 2 weeks for Saxion UAS. The main challenge of the game is collaborating with another person to control a single character, making it go up platforms, dodging dangerous lasers and barbed wires, and eventually escape the crazy laboratory.\nMy responsibilities for the project were game design, UX/UI and team management. It was the first time I took the initiative to be the team leader, coordinate the work of all roles and make sure the final product is polished. During the duration of the project, I learned the pipeline of the other roles and made sure it runs smoothly.",
